    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 features the high-revving S54 inline-six engine, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Engineered for the purist, it boasts a variable M differential lock and a chassis that has received critical subframe reinforcement and VANOS solenoid servicing. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering the communicative feedback and lateral stability expected of the chassis. With an 8,000 RPM redline and a meticulously maintained valvetrain, this specimen represents a mechanically sound example of Bavarian performance engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
