    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. This car has been a dependable daily driver, and it shows in its consistent performance. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though you'll find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a car that\u2019s actually been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, and all electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. I have a comprehensive service history showing regular oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
