      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive reliability and performance. This vehicle has been maintained to a high standard, offering a refined driving experience and a well-preserved interior. Each mechanical system has undergone a comprehensive evaluation to ensure continued peak performance and safety. For the professional seeking a sophisticated balance of value and enduring quality, this offering represents a superior investment in daily transportation.",
