    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s ready for her next adventure! This car has been super well-loved and is in really solid shape, running smoothly and looking great. It\u2019s been incredibly reliable for me, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it just as much. It\u2019s the perfect blend of comfort and dependability\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
