      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L flat-six powerplant, delivering linear power delivery through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, with the suspension geometry providing the communicative feedback Porsche is known for. Recent preventative maintenance includes an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal, ensuring the long-term integrity of the M96 architecture. The factory-spec limited-slip differential remains tight, and the braking system retains its firm pedal feel with cross-drilled rotors. While the finish shows light signs of road use consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil pressure and coolant temperature\u2014remain rock solid under load.",
